    "These tools allow the AI to store, recall, and manage important information from conversations for better context awareness." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Diese Tools ermöglichen der KI, wichtige Informationen aus Unterhaltungen zu speichern, abzurufen und zu verwalten, um den Kontext zu verbessern."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "These tools allow the AI to store, recall, and manage important information from conversations for better context awareness."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Estas herramientas permiten a la IA guardar, recordar y gestionar información importante de las conversaciones para mejor contexto."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ces outils permettent à l’IA de stocker, rappeler et gérer des informations importantes issues des conversations pour un meilleur contexte."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "これらのツールで AI は会話の重要情報を保存・呼び出し・管理し、文脈理解を向上させます。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이 도구로 AI가 대화의 중요한 정보를 저장·조회·관리하여 더 나은 컨텍스트 인식을 합니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这些工具允许 AI 存储、回忆和管理对话中的重要信息，以提供更佳的上下文感知能力。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These tools can only be used by models that support tool calls, and whether to use them is determined by the model." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
